data.description: CHAIN OF LAKES!! WATERFRONT!!BRING FISHING POLE! CHAIN OF LAKES WATERFRONT….4 BEDROOMS A GEM AMONGST ALL THE INVENTORY!!!  Ready to Venture to the ocean if you dare from this canal wide and deep. Chain of lakes that leads up to Lake Harris, Lake Eustis and other surrounding Lakes. FISH FROM YOUR OWN BACKYARD!  Master bedroom features one walk in closet and two full size wall closets…plus linen closet! Oversized master bath with glass walk-in shower and raised vanity with double sinks & granite counters. Split bedroom plan leads you to bedrooms 3 & 4 that share updated guest bath with new raised vanity with marble countertops and tub/shower combination. Huge bedroom 2 with large wall closet with separate sitting area. Home has been completely remodeled interior in year 2021…to include Kitchen with new solid wood cabinets, designer high end granite counter tops, large island, custom marble tile backsplash, under-counter lighting plus stainless-steel appliances side/side refrigerator with ice maker, smooth top range & dishwasher. Front lawn was also refreshed and renewed. Fresh new Grass in front of house. Living/dining area/ kitchen combo gives you a very open spacious feeling that leads into a separate den/office-screen porch with deck wood floors. Low HOA fees only $500/year calculated to $41.67/month.  In year 2017 seller replaced Roof with architectural shingles, replaced HVAC (air/heat) and had engineer structurally repair settlement issue ($42,000 cost) to insure stability of home with (per seller) transferable warranty! Oversized attached garage provides lots of storage. Upgraded electric circuit panel, replaced hot water heater and new drain field approx. 2018…Additional upgrades to include front windows Hurricane shutters, crown molding throughout and “wood look” tile floors…no carpet! Its time for your offer before its gone!!
